This is a **preload landing page** designed to enhance user experience while the main [Movie Recommendation App](https://your-render-app.onrender.com) (hosted on [Render](https://render.com)) **wakes up** from cold start. Free-tier Render apps can go idle after inactivity â€” this preloader offers a clean, cinematic â€œloadingâ€ screen and redirects users smoothly once the app is ready.

